17:21.119 --> 17:25.477
"Only a real risk can
test the reality of a belief."

17:25.680 --> 17:28.247
So, you're gonna risk our future over your yearbook quote?

17:28.440 --> 17:31.796
Josh, why am I here?

17:32.000 --> 17:34.434
Hello, earth to Josh.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.915
Why am I, Salutatorian of our graduating class,

17:37.120 --> 17:38.917
here at my
third-choice school?

17:39.160 --> 17:40.559
I'm sorry for having the next 50 years

17:40.760 --> 17:42.193
of our life planned out.

17:42.400 --> 17:43.799
That's just who I am.

17:44.040 --> 17:45.439
I don't know, Kara,
it's just--

17:45.640 --> 17:47.774
Josh, I love you, but I absolutely forbid you

17:47.840 --> 17:49.637
