You're taller than me.

18:21.400 --> 18:22.799
You're man enough to handle it.

18:23.000 --> 18:25.594
I'm just saying, I don't want
to be the short guy at the prom.

18:25.800 --> 18:27.233
Mr. Robertson!

18:27.440 --> 18:28.873
Hi, or should I call you Willie?

18:29.120 --> 18:30.519
You can call me Willie.

18:30.720 --> 18:32.312
Amy Ryan,
I blog "The New Left."

18:32.520 --> 18:33.953
Can I ask you a few questions?

18:34.160 --> 18:35.559
Yeah, sure, fire away.
This is my wife--

18:35.800 --> 18:37.153
Korie, I know.

18:37.360 --> 18:39.157
I'm actually surprised to see you here.

18:39.360 --> 18:45.276
I thought you'd be home, barefoot and pregnant.

18:45.480 --> 18:48.199
I haven't been barefoot and
pregnant in a really long time.

18:48.400 --> 18:49.833
I do kinda miss those days, huh?

18:50.040 --> 18:51.678
Yeah, you want to start
again? We can try.

18:51.880 --> 18:53.359
No.

18:53.560 --> 18:54.994
You've made a fortune selling devices

18:55.200 --> 18:58.078
